verbose_text: Ox and its precursor Iz were minor oxidation products.61 A thermolabile naphthalene endoperoxide derivative N, N '-di (2,3-dihydroxypropyl) -1,4-naphthalene-dipropanamide (DHPNO 2) (DHPNO 2 decomposes to 1 O 2 at 37 degreesC) was used to generate [18 O]-labeled singlet oxygen for delineation of mechanistic aspects of singlet oxygen mediated oxidation products of dG.
